    "p": [
      "Verify the user's identity before performing a requested password reset.",
      "The user's identity should be verified before performing a requested password reset to ensure that an attacker is not pretending to be the user to gain access.",
      "Add a requirement to the password policy to verify the user's identity when performing a requested password reset. Design and implement procedures for verifying the user's identity. For example, a user’s identity may be verified by meeting in person."
