  "html": "<h1>Applies to</h1>\n  <ul>\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 8.5.2</li>\n  </ul>\n  <h1>What to Do</h1>\n  <p>Verify the user's identity before performing a requested password reset.</p>\n  <h1>Why</h1>\n  <p>The user's identity should be verified before performing a requested password reset to ensure that an attacker is not pretending to be the user to gain access.</p>\n  <h1>How</h1>\n  <p>Add a requirement to the password policy to verify the user's identity when performing a requested password reset. Design and implement procedures for verifying the user's identity. For example, a user’s identity may be verified by meeting in person.</p>"
